quran[60]{c,v,t}:
  30,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim: yewtere sugu ﾉ容e Aayeeje yawtiino ka fuﾉ遼熔rde cortewol Al-Baqarah."
  30,2,"Faarisiyankooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n foolii Ruumi'en."
  30,3,"Nde fooleede waﾉ擁i ka Saami ka ﾉ砥ri ﾉ殿dorde leydi Faarisi ndin. Ruumiyankooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n non, ﾉ殿awo ﾉ兎 fooleede, ﾉ兎 fooloyay kamﾉ兎 kadi."
  30,4,"Ngol kiitol ko waﾉ擁, ko e dumunna mo hewtaa duuﾉ妬 tati o fawaa e duuﾉ妬 sappo. Ko Alla woodani fiyaaku on fow ado poolgal Ruumiyakooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ngal e ﾉ殿awo maggal. Nden ﾃｱalnde nde Ruumiyankooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n fooloyta Faarisiyankooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n weltoray."
  30,5,"ﾆ‘ weltorayay ko Alla walliri Ruumiyankooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n kon, tawde ﾉ兎n ko yimﾉ兎 Defte. Alla no walla on Mo O muuyani e jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n. Ko Kanko woni Fooluﾉ熔 Mo fooleaake, Hinnotooﾉ熔 jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  30,6,"Ngal balla ko fodoore Alla wonunoo. Laatagol mayre ngol ﾉ兎yday gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n pellital e fodoore Alla nden. Kono ko ﾉ砥ri ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de e yimﾉ兎 hino majjiraa ﾉ蓉m sabu keeferaaku maﾉ橡兎 ngun."
  30,7,"ﾆ‘ anndaa gomﾉ擁nal e ﾃｱaawooje sari'a. Ko ﾉ兎 anndii woo ko ko feeﾃｱi e nguurndam aduna ﾉ預m e ko yowondiri e ﾉ預ﾉ橡兎re nguuree maﾉ橡兎 e mahugol ngaddamaaku. Kono kamﾉ兎 e fii laakara on wonﾉ熔 hoﾉ熔 nguurndam ﾉ預m tigi, ko ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉urnii ﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 tefataa fii mun."
  30,8,"E ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎 fennooﾉ兎 miijitaaki fii no Alla tagiri wonkiiji maﾉ橡兎 O fotindiri ﾉ擁? Alla tagiraali kammuli ﾉ擁n e leydi ndin si wanaa goona, O tagiraali ﾉ擁 fijindaaru, O waﾉ預nii ﾉ擁 kadi lajal happaangal heddagol ka aduna. Anndee non, ko ﾉ砥ri ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ko yedduﾉ兎 hawroygol e Joomi maﾉ橡兎 ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, ko ﾉ蓉m haﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 hebloranagol nden ﾃｱalnde golle moﾆｴﾆｴe weltinayﾉ容 Joomi maﾉ橡兎."
  30,9,"E ﾉ兎e yiilaaki ka leydi ﾉ兎 taskoo ko honno battane mofte fennunooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ado maﾉ橡兎 wa'unoo? ﾆ‘n laatino ﾉ砥rﾉ兎 doole, ﾉ兎 wuurniti leydi ndin remuruuji, ﾉ兎 wuuri e mayri ﾉ砥ri ko ﾉ兎e wuuri e mayri kon. Nulaaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n addani ﾉ兎 hujjaaji ﾉ殿nnginﾉ擁 gootaaku Alla ngun, kono ﾉ兎 fenni. Alla tooﾃｱiraa ﾉ兎 halkugol ﾉ兎 ngol, kono non, ko ko'e maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎 wonunoo e tooﾃｱirde jolnorgol jolirde halkaare sabu keefaraagu maﾉ橡兎 ngun ."
  30,10,"Refti ko wonunoo battane ﾉ兎n bonnirnooﾉ兎 golle mun sirkangol Alla e golle bonﾉ容, ko bone ﾉ砥rﾉ熔 bondne; tawde ﾉ兎 fennii Aayeeje Alla ﾉ容n, ﾉ兎 laatii e jalkitugol ﾉ容."
  30,11,"Ko Alla woni fuﾉ遼擁rﾉ熔 tagu ngun no ngu ko aldah e yeru gadiiﾉ熔, refti O gayna fii maggu, refti O ruttita ngu; refti ko ka Makko Kanko tun rutteteﾉ熔n ﾃ疎lnde Darngal fii hasbeede yoﾉ兎e."
  30,12,"ﾃ疎lnde Darngal ngal dorotoo, bombe ﾉ兎n taﾆｴoyto e yurmeende Alla, tawde hujja maﾉ橡兎 e yeddugol Alla ngol wonii bolle puyﾉ容."
  30,13,"Woodanoytaaﾉ兎 e kafidiiﾉ擁 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎 rewynoo ﾉ擁n aduna, ko tefana ﾉ兎 daﾉ蓉gol lepte ﾉ容n, wurin ﾉ擁n yeddoyay kafiduﾉ兎ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎n; ﾉ擁 hoynoya ﾉ兎 ka ﾉ兎 hatonjinnoo e maﾉ橡兎, kono ﾉ擁 hattanaa e, tawde ﾉ兎 fotay ka halkaare."
  30,14,"ﾃ疎lnde Darngal ngal darii, nden ﾃｱalnde yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n sertiroyay e njoﾉ電i yeru no ﾉ兎 gollirnoo aduna non: woﾉ遼兎 towniroyee ka Aljannaaji dow, woﾉ遼兎 jippiniroyee ley ka Yiite."
  30,15,"Si ko ﾉ兎n gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 Alla ﾉ兎 golli golle moﾆｴﾆｴe weltinayﾉ容 Mo, ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔n wonoyay e beeli Aljanna hiﾉ兎 weltiro ko ﾉ兎 neeminirtee ton e neemaaji duumotooﾉ擁 poomaa."
  30,16,"Si tawii non ko ﾉ兎n yedduﾉ兎 Alla ﾉ兎 fenni Aayeeje Amen jippinaaﾉ容 e Nulaaﾉ兎 Amen ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎 fenni kadi ummital e hasboore, ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔n ko tawnoyteeﾉ兎 e lepte ﾉ容n ﾉ兎 lutta e majje."
  30,17,"Subbuhinanee Alla tuma naatanton kiikiiﾉ容; ﾉ蓉m woni fewndo julde futuroo e geeﾆｴe, subbunhinanoﾉ熔n Mo kadi tuma naatanton bimmbi; ﾉ蓉m ko fewndo julde subaka nden."
  30,18,"Ko Kanko Alla tun mantoore woodani: Malaa'ika'en no yetta Mo ka kammuuli, tagu ngun kadi no yettira Mo ka leydi. Subbunhinane Mo saanga naatanton kiikiiﾉ容, ﾉ蓉m woni fewndo ka Alansaraa, subbunhinanﾉ熔n Mo kadi saanga ﾃｱallonton, ﾉ蓉m woni fewndo ka fanaa."
  30,19,"Himo yaltina ko wuuri e nder ko maayi; wano tagirgol neﾉ遼熔 immorde e toﾉ橡兎re maniiyu maa yaltinirgol cofun e nder woofoonde, Himo yaltina kadi ko maayi e nder ko wuuri, wano tagirgol Mo toﾉ橡兎re maniiyu nden immorde e neﾉ遼熔 maa woofoonde nden immorde e gertogal ngal. Himo wuurnitira leydi ndin jippingol toﾉ登 fuﾉ擁na ndi ﾉ殿awo ndi yoorude. Ko wano ndin leydi wuurnitiraa non fuﾉ擁ngol ndi, yaltinirteﾉ熔n e genaale maon fii hasbeede yoﾉ兎e."
  30,20,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Alla mawﾉ擁 tinndinﾉ擁 kattal Makko ngal e gootankaaku Makko ngun: wonde O tagii mon onon ﾉ兎e yimﾉ兎, immorde e mbum-mbuldi, fewndo O tagirnoo ben Aadama e loopal, refti jaka ko on ﾉ殿nndinke saakitorayﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉uﾉ預l, saakitoﾉ熔n hiirnaange e fuﾉ溶aange leydi ndin."
  30,21,"Hino jeyaa fahin e maandeeji Alla mawﾉ擁 tinndinay- ﾉ擁 kattal e gootaaku Makko, wonnde O taganii on, onon worﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, immorde e noone mon, resondir- ﾉ兎, fii yo on deeﾆｴir e maﾉ橡兎 tawde ko on noone gooto, O waﾉ擁 hakkunde mon giggol e yurmeende. Wonii e ko jantaa koo, hujjaaji ﾉ殿nnguﾉ擁 wonannde yimﾉ兎 miijitotooﾉ兎, tawde ko kamﾉ兎 nafitorta gollitirgol haqqil."
  30,22,"Hino jeyaa kadi e maandeeji Alla ﾉ擁n tinndinﾉ擁 kattal e gootaaku Makko, tagugol kammuuli ﾉ擁n e leydi ndin, e luutondirgol haalaaji mon e nooneeji mon. Wonii e ko jantaa koo, hujjaaji ﾉ殿nnganﾉ擁 yimﾉ兎 anndal e tasakuyee ﾉ兎n."
  30,23,"Hino jeyaa kadi e maandeeji Makko mawﾉ擁 tinnin- ﾉ擁 kattal e gootaaku Makko: ﾉ熔yngol mon ngol jemma e ﾃｱalorma, fii fowtagol e ronkere golle mon. Hino jeyaa e majji fahin, ko O waﾉ擁rani on ﾃｱalorma on kon saakitagol e makko ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬ra Joomi mon arsike. Wonii e ko jantaa koo, hujjaaji ﾉ殿nnguﾉ擁, wonannde yimﾉ兎 nanooﾉ兎 nanugol taskoo e nanugol jaﾉ電e."
  30,24,"Hino jeyaa kadi e maandeeji Makko mawﾉ擁t inndi- tnayﾉ擁 kattal e gootaaku Makko, hollirgol on maﾆｴe ﾉ容n ka kammu; O hawtitana on e ﾉ蓉m, hakkunde kulol parﾃｱite ﾉ容n e tama'u toﾉ登 ngon. Himo jippini- ra kadi ka kammu ndiyam toﾉ登, O wuurnitira ﾉ預m leydi ndin, fuﾉ擁ngol puﾉ擁 e mayri, ﾉ殿awo ndi yoorde Wonii e ko jantaa koo, hujjaaji ﾉ殿nnguﾉ擁, wonande yimﾉ兎 haqqilooﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 dallinora ﾉ蓉m ummital ﾉ殿awo maayde, fii hasbeede yoﾉ兎e."
  30,25,"Hino jeyaa e maandeji Makko tindinﾉ擁 kattal e gootaaku Makko: tawde kammu ngun e leydi ndin no darorii yamiroore Makko ko aldaa e yanugol. Refti si o noddii noddaandu wutttugol Mala'ikaajo on allaandu ndu ka leydi, e jaka onon hiﾉ熔n yaltira e genaale mon ﾉ容n hasbeede yoﾉ兎e."
  30,26,"Ko kanko tun woodani, laamagol e tagugol e toppital ﾉ兎n wonﾉ兎 ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Kala kon ko tagaa, ko ﾉ熔ftiiﾉ兎 Mo jebbilanii yamiroore Makko."
  30,27,"Ko Kanko woni fuﾉ遼熔rﾉ熔 tagugol ngol no ko aldah, e yeru gadiiﾉ熔 refti O ruttita ngu ﾉ殿awo gaynugol fii maggu. Awa fuﾉ遼擁tagol ngol hino ﾉ砥ri fuﾉ遼預gol ngol welde fii, fow mun, ﾉ擁n ﾉ擁ﾉ擁 kala hino newanii Alla; tawde si O faandanike huunde, O daalanay nde tun: "Laato", nde laatoo. Hino woodani Mo Kanko tedduﾉ熔 mawﾉ熔 On, sifa ﾉ砥rﾉ熔 toowude on e kala ko O sifortee e sifaaji mawngu e timmal. Ko Kanko woni Fooluﾉ熔 Mo fooletaak, ﾃ粗eﾃｱuﾉ熔 e tagu Mun e toppitagol Mun."
  30,28,"O piyanii on misal, onon ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎, ﾆｴettaangal e mon: Hara no woodani on e maccuﾉ兎 mon ﾉ兎n e ﾉ兎n jeytirﾉ熔n ﾃｱaame mon renndaaﾉ熔 e jawle mon ﾉ容n, ﾉ兎 huloton senndodugol ﾉ容n jewle e mon, wano hulirton senndodugol e dimo hawtiduﾉ熔 e mon jawle? Hara on jaﾉ殿nay ﾉ蓉m maccuﾉ熔 mon? Pellet on jaﾉ殿taa ﾉ蓉m. Awa ko Alla ﾉ砥ri hanndude nde O jaﾉ殿taa kafideede e tagu Makko (jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n) ka laamu Makko. Ko wano ngal misal piyirani mon, ngam Men ﾉ殿nngina hujjaaji e ﾉ殿nngannduyeeji sertuﾉ擁, wonnde yimﾉ兎 haqqilﾉ兎, tawde ko kamﾉ兎 nafitorta ﾉ蓉m."
  30,29,"Wanaa waasde dalil woni sabu majjere maﾉ橡兎, wanaa waaseede ﾉ殿nnginannede kadi. Majjere maﾉ橡兎 nden, ko sabu jokkugol mbeleeﾉ容 e ﾃｱemmbugol baabiraaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎. Ko hommbo non fewnata mo Alla majjini? Hay gooto! Alanaa ﾉ兎 wallooﾉ兎 ko duﾃｱana ﾉ兎 lepte Alla ﾉ容n."
  30,30,"Fewtiniri yeeso maa ngon, an Nulaaﾉ熔 e wondu- ﾉ兎 e maa ﾉ兎n, e diina Alla kan; acca kala diina si wanaa diina Makko kan. ﾆ隔m ko diina lislaamu mo Alla tagiri yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e mun. Waﾉ葉itugol alaa e tagu Alla ngun. Ko ﾉ蓉m woni diina focciika kan; kono ﾉ砥rﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de e yimﾉ兎 anndaa wonnde ko ﾉ蓉m woni diina goonga."
  30,31,"Ruttoree e Makko tuubugol e junuubi mon, huliron Mo ﾉ熔ftagol yamirooje Makko woﾉ遼擁too haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko, ﾃｱinniron julde nden no timmiri, wata on jeye e sirkooﾉ兎 lunndiiﾉ兎 tagoodi ndin; ﾉ兎 kafida Alla e woﾉ遼兎 goo ka dewe maﾉ橡兎,"
  30,32,"Wata on wa'u wa ﾉ兎n sirkooﾉ兎 waylunooﾉ兎 diina mun, ﾉ兎 goomﾉ擁ni yoga ﾉ兎 yeddi yoga, ﾉ兎 wonti pecce-pecce, fedde kala e maﾉ橡兎 no weltora meere wonnde ka maﾉ橡兎 nden, kala yi'a ko kaﾃｱum tun woni e goonga, ﾉ兎ya kan ko e meere woni."
  30,33,"Si saﾉ葉eende memii sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, immorde e ﾃｱawu maa baasal maa kokke, ﾉ兎 nodda Joomi maﾉ橡兎 tun, ruttitorgol e Makko yankinagol moolo e makko, fii no O huncirana ﾉ兎 saﾉ葉eende maﾉ橡兎. Hooti si O yurmiraama ﾉ兎 huncangol ﾉ兎 nden saﾉ葉eende, e jaka fedde e maﾉ橡兎 hino yiltitoo e sirkangol kafida Joomi mun e goﾉ遼蓉m goo ka du'agol."
  30,34,"Si ﾉ兎 yeddi neemaaji Alla ﾉ擁n, wano yeddugol ﾉ兎 neema huncaneede saﾉ葉eende nden, wonii ﾉ兎 dakmitorii ko ﾉ兎 jogitii e ﾉ預m nguurndam, arma ﾉ兎 yi'iroya gite maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, wonnde ko e majjere ﾉ殿nngunde ﾉ兎 wonunoo e mun."
  30,35,"Ko naadi ﾉ兎 e sirkangol Alla ko aldaa e hujja? Menen, Men jippinaali e maﾉ橡兎 hujja Deftere, mo ﾉ兎 dallinorta e ko ﾉ兎 sirkanta Alla kon. ﾆ‘ alaa kadi deftere yewtaynde fii sirku maﾉ橡兎 on, qirritantoonde ﾉ兎 sellugol ko ﾉ兎 yeddaynoo kon."
  30,36,"Si Men meeﾉ擁nirii yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n gootel e neemaaji Amen ﾉ擁n, wano cellal e ngalu, ﾉ兎 weltora ﾉ蓉m weltaare dullere e townitaare. Si tawnii non ko bone on memirii ﾉ兎 - wano ﾃｱawu e baasal - sabu ko juuﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n faggitori kon geddi, ﾉ蓉m haray ﾉ兎 taﾆｴike yurmeende Alla nden, ﾉ兎 sikka ﾉ蓉m ﾉ熔n iwataa e maﾉ橡兎."
  30,37,"E ﾉ兎e yi'aali, wonnde Alla no yaﾃｱﾃｱana arsike on mo O muuyani e jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, fii ndaarnda- gol ﾉ兎 si ﾉ兎 yettay Mo maa si ﾉ兎 yedday? Himo ﾉ妬ﾉ葉inana Mo kadi on Mo O muuyani e maﾉ橡兎, fii anndugol si o muﾃｱﾃｱoto maa o muﾃｱﾃｱoo? Wonii e ﾉ蓉m, maandeeji wonannde gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 neweende e yurmeende Alla nden."
  30,38,"An juulﾉ熔 on, jonnu jom-ﾉ殿dal ngal ko o haandi ko, ka moﾆｴﾆｴugol e ka jokkugol enﾉ預m, okkaa hatonjinﾉ熔 kadi ko humtanta mo haaju mum, walla-ﾉ預a tumarankeejo woﾉ遼擁tiiﾉ熔 leydi mun. Ko ngool okkugol e ﾉ容en geece ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴude wonande ﾉ兎n faalaaﾉ兎 yarluyee Alla on; ko ﾉ兎n huntooﾉ兎 ﾉ擁n haajuuji kadi, woni maliroyteeﾉ兎 heﾉ砥gol Aljanna mo ﾉ兎 ﾉ預ﾉ橡殿ynoo, ﾉ兎 hisa e lepte ﾉ容 ﾉ兎 hulunoo."
  30,39,"Kala ko jonnirﾉ熔n yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e jawle, fii no ﾉ容 artira e mon ﾉ兎ydaari(riba), annde ﾉ容 ﾉ兎ydotaako ka Alla. Kala non ko jonnirﾉ熔n e jawle mon ﾉ容n, fii ko duncitoree haaju, hara hiﾉ熔n ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬ra ﾉ蓉m yarluyee Alla, wanaa darja maa manteede, ko ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔n woni sowanoyteeﾉ兎 njoﾉ電i ka Alla."
  30,40,"Ko Alla gooto On hertori tagugol on, refti arsikugol on, refti warugol on wuurnita. Hara no e sanamuuji mon, ﾉ擁 rewoton gaanin Makko ﾉ擁n, waﾉ預yndu goﾉ遼蓉m e ﾉ擁n? Senayee woodanii Mo! O toowii e ko sirkooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wowlata ﾉ兎 fiﾉ殿."
  30,41,"Bone on feeﾃｱirii ka njorndi e ka maaje, ﾉ蓉ytagol nguurndam yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e wonkiiji maﾉ橡兎, nawnaaje e ﾃｱabbuuli; sabu ko ﾉ兎 golli e geddi. ﾆ隔m feeﾃｱirii fii no Alla meeﾉ擁nira ﾉ兎 njoﾉ電i yoga e ko ﾉ兎 bonnuno e nguurndam aduna ﾉ預m; belajo'o, ﾉ兎 ruttoray e Makko tuubugol."
  30,42,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, maakan ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎: Yiilee ka leydi, taskoﾉ熔n ko honno battane mofte fennunooﾉ兎 adinooﾉ兎 on ﾉ兎n wa'unoo. ﾆ隔m ko battane bonﾉ容 wonunoo, tawde ko ﾉ砥ri ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de e maﾉ橡兎 ko sirkanaynooﾉ兎 Alla, ﾉ兎 halkiraa sabu ﾉ蓉m."
  30,43,"An Nulaaﾉ熔, fewtinir yeeso maa ngon e diina lislaamu focciika kan, ado ﾃ疎lnde Darngal arde nde ruttoowo nde alaa. Nden ﾃｱalnde, yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n seedoya: fedde goo neeminiree ka Aljanna, ndeya fedde leptiroyee ka Yiite."
  30,44,"Kala yedduﾉ熔 Alla, lorra mun - woni luttugol ka Yiite - ko e makko yantata. Kala non golluﾉ熔 moﾆｴﾆｴere, nde o ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬ri welayee Alla e mun, haray ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔n, ko ko'e-maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎 hebilani naatugol Aljanna, ﾉ兎 neeminora duumagol ton poomaa."
  30,45,"Ko fii no Alla yoﾉ妬ra gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 Mo ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎 golli moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ擁 welayﾉ擁 Joomi maﾉ橡兎. Pellet, Kanko seniiﾉ熔 On, O yiﾉ預a yeddiduﾉ兎 Mo e Nulaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, hiﾉ兎 metta Mo sanne, O leptoyay ﾉ兎 ﾃ疎lnde Darngal."
  30,46,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Alla mawﾉ擁, tinnﾉ擁nayﾉ擁 kattal e gootaaku Makko, wurtugol Mo keneeli wewlinirayﾉ擁 jeyaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, hewtugol toﾉ登 ngon, e fii yo O meeﾉ擁nir on, onon yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, yurmeende Makko nden, heﾉ砥gol moﾆｴﾆｴere toﾉ登 ngon, woni ... O waﾉ擁ri ﾉ蓉m kadi, no laaﾉ容 ﾉ容n dogira muuyaaﾉ容 Makko, e fii no ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬ron e ﾉ砥ral Makko ngal, ngeygu ka maaje, belajo'o, on yettay neemaaji Alla ﾉ擁n e mooﾉ熔n, O ﾉ兎ydana on."
  30,47,"Gomﾉ擁i Men nulii ado maa an Nulaaﾉ熔, Nulaaﾉ兎 goo, haa e mofte maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, ﾉ兎 addani ﾉ兎 hujjaaji ﾉ殿nnginﾉ擁 gonnga maﾉ橡兎 kan, kono ﾉ兎ya fenni ﾉ兎. Men yottii ontuma e ﾉ兎n faggitiiﾉ兎 geddi, Men halkiri ﾉ兎 lepte Amen ﾉ容n, Men daﾉ溶di Nulaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 wondunooﾉ兎 e maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n. Daﾉ溶dugol gomﾉ擁me ﾉ兎n, faaboo ﾉ兎, ko ko Men waﾉ遼擁ni e Amen."
  30,48,"Ko Alla woni nuloowo immina keneeli ﾉ擁n, ﾉ擁 sogga duule ﾉ容n; O saakitira ﾉ蓉m ka weeyo no O muuyiri, ﾉ蓉uﾉ擁 fanﾉ擁; O waﾉ葉a ﾉ蓉m taﾆｴe-taﾆｴe. A yi'ay ontuma, an ndaaroowo on, toﾉ登 ngon no yalta hakkunde mun. Si O hewtinii toﾉ登 ngon e on Mo O muuyi e jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, e jaka hiﾉ兎 weltora yurmeende Alla nden e maﾉ橡兎, woni heﾉ砥gol toﾉ登, leydi ndin fuﾉ擁na ko ﾉ兎 haajitora kamﾉ兎 e neemoraaﾉ擁 maﾉ橡兎."
  30,49,"Gomﾉ擁i ﾉ兎 laatinoke ado Alla jippinde toﾉ登 ngon e maﾉ橡兎, ko ﾉ兎 taﾆｴinooﾉ兎 e ﾉ蓉m."
  30,50,"Ndaarii an Nulaaﾉ熔, battane toﾉ登 ngo Alla jippiniri yurmeende e jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, no O wuurnitirta leydi ndin noone e puﾉ擁, ﾉ殿awo ndii cojjii ndi yoori. Pellet, waﾉ蓉ﾉ熔 ﾉ蓉m On, ko wuurnitoowo maayﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, Kanko ko O hattanﾉ熔 kala huunde, huunde ronkintaa Mo."
  30,51,"sI Men nulii henndu e gese maa e puﾉ擁 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n ko bonna fii mun, ﾉ兎 yi'i ﾉ容n gese maﾉ橡兎 no soyﾉ預 ﾉ殿awo nde ﾉ容 hecciﾉ蓉noo, ﾉ兎 waﾉ葉inay ﾉ殿awo ﾉ蓉m, ko ﾉ兎 yeddooﾉ兎 neemaaji Alla yawtuﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n, e ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉gol majji."
  30,52,"Ko wano woniri non a nanintaa maayﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e faaﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, woﾉ遼擁torii ﾉ兎 ma fii wata ﾉ兎 nane few, ko wano non woniri a waawataa fewnude nanndo maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ蓉urnﾉ擁iﾉ熔 saliiﾉ熔 heﾉ擁taade."
  30,53,"A wonaali fewnoo mo Alla majjini e laawol focciingol ngol, a nanintaa ko nafata, si wanaa on gomﾉ擁inﾉ熔 Aayeeje Amen ﾉ容n, tawde ko kanko nafitorta ko wowlata, ﾉ兎n, ko jebbilaniiﾉ兎 Men, yankiniiﾉ兎."
  30,54,"Ko Alla woni taguﾉ熔 on, onon ﾉ兎e yimﾉ兎, immorde e ndihal hoykal, refi O waﾉ擁 ﾉ殿awo lo'ere mon entereyaagal nden, cemmbe sagatalaaku, refi O waﾉ擁 ﾉ殿awo ﾉ容n cemmbe, lo'ere nayeegu. Alla hino taga ko O yiﾉ擁, immorde e ko lo'i maa ko dolni. Ko Kano woni Annduﾉ熔 kala huunde, huunde ronkintaa Mo. Hattanﾉ熔 Mo huunde ronkintaa."
  30,55,"ﾃ疎lnde Darangal ngal drotoo, bomﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n huﾉ熔to ﾉ兎 ﾃｱiiﾉ殿ali ka genaale maﾉ橡兎 si wanaa saanga. Ko wano ﾉ兎 ferlisiraa e anndugol happu ﾃｱiiﾉ砥gol maﾉ橡兎 ngol ka genaale, ﾉ兎 wonanoo e firliteede aduna, gaayi e goonga."
  30,56,"ﾆ‘n Annabaaﾉ兎 e Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 Alla okki ganndal ﾉ兎n wi'a: Gomﾉ擁i on ﾃｱiiﾉ妬i e ko Alla winndi kon e ganndal Makko ngal, gila ﾃｱalnde tagaﾉ熔n haa ﾃｱalde ummital mon ngal yedduﾉ熔n. Kono onon on anndaano wonnde ummital ko waﾉ預yﾉ蓉m, yedduﾉ熔n ﾉ蓉m."
  30,57,"ﾃ疎lnde Alla immintinoyta tagu ngun, fii hasbeede yoﾉ妬tee, ngantooji ﾉ擁 tooﾃｱuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n fefindoytoo ﾉ擁n nafoytaa ﾉ兎, wanaa kamﾉ兎 woni ko ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬rtee weltingol Alla, sakko ﾉ兎 jaﾉ殿nee tuubugol ruttoo e Makko, tawde haray laawiki!"
  30,58,"Gomﾉ擁i Men piyanii yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e ndee Alqur'aanaare, ko toppitagol fii maﾉ橡兎, kala misal. ﾆ隔m, ko fii no goonga feeﾃｱirana ﾉ兎 e nder meere nden. Pellet, si a addanii ﾉ兎, an Nulaaﾉ熔, hujja goonga maa kan, ma ﾉ兎n yedduﾉ兎 Alla wi'u: On wonaali, si wanaa meerenteeﾉ兎 e ko adduﾉ熔n kon."
  30,59,"Ko wano ﾉ兎rﾉ容 ﾉ兎e ﾉ兎 tawata si a addaniiﾉ兎 Aaya ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁ntaa, Alla notiraa e ﾉ兎nrde kala ﾉ兎 anndaa wonnde ko addan-ﾉ預aﾉ兎 kon, ko goonga."
  30,60,"Muﾃｱﾃｱo an Nulaaﾉ熔, e ko yimﾉ兎 maa ﾉ兎n fennete kon. Anndaa pellet, fodoore Alla faabo e foolde, ko laatotooﾉ蓉m sikke alaa. Wata dunyma ﾉ兎 yananaaka e ummital ﾉ兎n duﾃｱe e hawjugol, ronkaa muﾃｱﾃｱaade."
